Class PreprocessableCommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.pagekite.glen3b.library.bukkit.command.PreprocessableCommand
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.bukkit.event.Listener

    public final class PreprocessableCommand
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.bukkit.event.Listener
    Represents a command that can be processed by the PlayerCommandPreprocessEvent, which will be registered at highest priority.

    Glen Husman
